          <p>Keep and showcase your biggest catches. You'll also earn coins based on how good they are.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rightColumn">
        <picture>
          <source srcset="../images/web/aquarium.webp" type="image/webp">
          <source srcset="../images/backup/aquarium.jpg" type="image/jpeg">
          <img id="aquariumImg" src="../images/web/aquarium.webp" alt="aquarium">
        </picture>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="row">
      <div class="leftColumn">
        <picture>
          <source srcset="../images/web/equipment.webp" type="image/webp">
          <source srcset="../images/backup/equipment.jpg" type="image/jpeg">
          <img src="../images/web/equipment.webp" alt="equipment">
        </picture>
      </div>
      <div class="rightColumn center">
        <div class="desc four">
          <h1>Your Equipment</h1>
          <p>Use coins to buy equipment and prepare yourself for bigger catches.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="footer">
      <div class="footerColumn">
